sourcesContent: import SwiperCore, { EffectCube, Pagination } from 'swiper' import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from 'swiper/react' import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardBody } from 'reactstrap' import img1 from '@Assets/images/banner/banner-21.jpg' import img2 from '@Assets/images/banner/banner-22.jpg' import img3 from '@Assets/images/banner/banner-23.jpg' import img4 from '@Assets/images/banner/banner-24.jpg' const params = { effect: 'cube', className: 'swiper-cube-effect', pagination: { clickable: true } } SwiperCore.use([EffectCube, Pagination]) const SwiperThreeD = ({ isRtl }) => { return ( 3D Cube Effect ) } export default SwiperThreeD
